  <h2>Overview and CQC Inspections</h2>
  <div class="modal-link"><a href="#icon-keys" id="modal-icon-keys-both">Click for key <img src="https://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/all/themes/cqc/images/status_ticks/green_tick_small.png" alt="Green Tick" title="Green Tick" /><img src="https://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/all/themes/cqc/images/status_ticks/grey_cross_small.png" alt="Grey Cross" title="Grey Cross" /><img class="red-cross" src="https://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/all/themes/cqc/images/status_ticks/red_cross_small.png" alt="Red Cross" title="Red Cross" /><img src="https://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/all/themes/cqc/images/smarties/star.png" alt="Star" title="Star" /><img src="https://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/all/themes/cqc/images/smarties/green.png" alt="Green smartie" title="Green smartie" /><img src="https://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/all/themes/cqc/images/smarties/yellow.png" alt="Yellow smartie" title="Yellow smartie" /><img src="https://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/all/themes/cqc/images/smarties/red.png" alt="Red smartie" title="Red smartie" /><img src="https://www.cqc.org.uk/sites/all/themes/cqc/images/smarties/grey.png" alt="Grey smartie" title="Grey smartie" /></a></div></div>
